data.actual_result: It doesn't autocorrect your sentence besides from giving you suggestions in the suggestion box
data.short_description: Autocorrect does not work in search and in the share modal at all, besides from the suggestion box
data.steps_to_repro: - Share an image to get the share modal - Type something grammatically wrong or a typo. For an example "im" instead of "I'm" it should autocorrect to "I'm" but it doesn't but instead only suggests it in the suggestion box in gboard - Try the following steps above as well for search.
